data.description: Renovated 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom home in Downtown Dickson! Kitchen and bathroom remodel, completely gutted in 2018. New roof and completely new HVAC system to include duct work, and new vapor Barrier in 2023. New Windows 2018. Other items new/replaced within last 6 years to include water heater, appliances, breaker box, interior doors, and flooring.  Great fenced yard! Two sheds/storage buildings to remain with the property. Great starter home or great for someone needing to downsize! Sellers have lived in home for 20 years! Seller is unable to accommodate showings during the hours of 9:00am- 4:30 pm Monday-Friday due to work schedule. Weekends can be shown anytime!
